1
00:00:21,260 --> 00:00:22,050
Hello.

2
00:00:25,260 --> 00:00:26,330
Is that Mo Yungao?

3
00:00:27,370 --> 00:00:29,170
All your men are dead.

4
00:00:32,740 --> 00:00:33,740
Who are you?

5
00:00:35,390 --> 00:00:37,930
Agent Zhang Haixia
of the Southern Archives.

6
00:00:39,970 --> 00:00:41,460
You killed all my men?

7
00:00:53,220 --> 00:00:54,750
A member of the Zhang family

8
00:00:56,500 --> 00:00:58,210
really didn't disappoint me.

9
00:00:58,230 --> 00:00:59,890
Thank you for telling me that.

10
00:01:01,520 --> 00:01:02,660
I have a

11
00:01:03,350 --> 00:01:05,550
very private question I want to ask you.

12
00:01:06,710 --> 00:01:07,350
Go ahead.

13
00:01:11,920 --> 00:01:13,480
Do you, like me,

14
00:01:14,380 --> 00:01:16,210
have an intense desire
to revel in other people's suffering

15
00:01:16,210 --> 00:01:18,960
at certain moments?

16
00:02:05,510 --> 00:02:06,230
I have.

17
00:02:09,340 --> 00:02:11,270
And if that desire never goes away,

18
00:02:13,300 --> 00:02:14,350
what would you do?

19
00:02:17,740 --> 00:02:18,770
Go along with it.

20
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:29,660
So from the beginning,

21
00:02:30,560 --> 00:02:32,020
you also had a conscience.

22
00:02:35,050 --> 00:02:37,579
When did that conscience
start to disappear?

23
00:02:43,450 --> 00:02:44,850
Where will people like us

24
00:02:48,970 --> 00:02:50,650
end up in the future?

25
00:02:54,410 --> 00:02:56,010
You have too many questions.

26
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:58,060
I don't want to answer.

27
00:02:58,820 --> 00:03:00,490
But I can tell you one thing—

28
00:03:00,580 --> 00:03:01,650
your destination.

29
00:03:02,870 --> 00:03:05,700
Your destination and mine

30
00:03:05,730 --> 00:03:07,330
are definitely not the same.

31
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:09,710
If you want to know your destination,

32
00:03:09,710 --> 00:03:11,170
you'd better come find me.

33
00:03:11,470 --> 00:03:12,360
But my condition is

34
00:03:12,360 --> 00:03:14,090
that you must become my friend.

35
00:03:16,620 --> 00:03:17,750
The choice is yours.

36
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:55,829
Just like that,

37
00:03:56,020 --> 00:03:58,079
Mo Yungao's Twilight Grass plan

38
00:03:58,430 --> 00:04:01,900
was completely destroyed

39
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:04,080
with the assistance
of Zhang Haiqi, Zhang Hailou,

40
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:05,780
Zhang Haixia, and Zhang Qishan.

41
00:04:05,780 --> 00:04:08,240
Tens of thousands of people in four cities

42
00:04:08,260 --> 00:04:09,880
were saved from the fire.

43
00:04:10,150 --> 00:04:11,860
Mo Yungao's warlord forces

44
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:14,810
were also quickly dismantled
in this incident.

45
00:04:15,060 --> 00:04:16,600
His reputation disappeared

46
00:04:16,600 --> 00:04:19,810
without a trace in a very short time.

47
00:05:43,510 --> 00:05:50,070
[Archives: The Nanyang Mystery]

48
00:05:50,420 --> 00:05:52,970
[Episode 22]

49
00:06:18,510 --> 00:06:21,380
[Xiacheng]

50
00:06:31,530 --> 00:06:32,530
Tell my fortune.

51
00:06:39,690 --> 00:06:40,920
I remember you.

52
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:44,390
You still owe me a silver dollar.

53
00:06:47,310 --> 00:06:48,840
I once asked you a question.

54
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:50,760
I had a thought in my mind—

55
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:52,810
should I kill it,

56
00:06:53,540 --> 00:06:54,540
or will it kill me?

57
00:06:55,860 --> 00:06:57,460
You told me to go with the flow

58
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:59,380
and act on what I truly wanted.

59
00:07:01,310 --> 00:07:02,940
So later,

60
00:07:03,190 --> 00:07:04,720
what did you choose?

61
00:07:31,330 --> 00:07:32,330
I don't want this.

62
00:07:35,730 --> 00:07:37,260
I'm not this kind of person.

63
00:07:37,800 --> 00:07:39,710
[Fortune-teller] [Face reading]

64
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:42,650
I shouldn't have survived.

65
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:47,540
I should be dead.

66
00:08:38,789 --> 00:08:39,510
You

67
00:08:40,270 --> 00:08:41,890
are Mo Yungao.

68
00:09:02,780 --> 00:09:03,710
What did you say?

69
00:09:04,250 --> 00:09:05,910
Is it that hard to understand?

70
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:07,930
Zhang Haixia used Twilight Grass

71
00:09:07,930 --> 00:09:09,520
to wipe out all Mo faction warlords.

72
00:09:09,450 --> 00:09:11,630
[Investigation Report]

73
00:09:09,630 --> 00:09:10,830
No one was left alive.

74
00:09:11,760 --> 00:09:14,270
Thanks to the fact that Great Master Buddha's
men are all from the Zhang family

75
00:09:14,270 --> 00:09:16,050
and have special physical constitutions,
they survived.

76
00:09:16,050 --> 00:09:17,010
Otherwise,

77
00:09:17,460 --> 00:09:19,260
they would all be dead this time.

78
00:09:22,440 --> 00:09:24,970
Our goal this time
is to wipe out Mo's faction.

79
00:09:26,510 --> 00:09:27,740
But Zhang Haixia

80
00:09:28,150 --> 00:09:29,550
was almost out of control

81
00:09:30,100 --> 00:09:31,430
during this operation.

82
00:09:32,260 --> 00:09:34,390
I need to interrogate him.

83
00:09:35,700 --> 00:09:36,840
But Zhang Haixia

84
00:09:37,750 --> 00:09:38,740
is missing.

85
00:09:39,410 --> 00:09:41,470
Great Master Buddha asked us for him.

86
00:09:41,940 --> 00:09:43,910
You took him away
without telling us before.

87
00:09:43,910 --> 00:09:44,670
Now he's missing,

88
00:09:44,670 --> 00:09:45,670
and you ask us for him?

89
00:09:45,670 --> 00:09:47,330
I should be asking you for him!

90
00:09:55,220 --> 00:09:56,020
Zhang Hailou,

91
00:10:01,030 --> 00:10:02,320
as for Zhang Haixia,

92
00:10:02,340 --> 00:10:04,150
I'll give Great Master Buddha
an explanation.

93
00:10:04,150 --> 00:10:06,280
But he's from the Archives, after all.

94
00:10:06,340 --> 00:10:08,670
How he should be
dealt with is my business.

95
00:10:08,700 --> 00:10:09,340
All right.

96
00:10:09,820 --> 00:10:12,230
Then I will wait for your news.

97
00:10:12,940 --> 00:10:13,650
However,

98
00:10:14,530 --> 00:10:16,530
if my men find him first,

99
00:10:17,860 --> 00:10:20,120
then don't blame me for showing no mercy.

100
00:10:26,840 --> 00:10:30,930
[Changxiang Rice Noodles]

101
00:10:27,250 --> 00:10:29,130
Take a look at the oil-paper umbrellas.

102
00:10:29,130 --> 00:10:30,730
They are sturdy and durable.

103
00:10:34,460 --> 00:10:36,390
Two bowls of noodles, extra spicy.

104
00:10:37,620 --> 00:10:39,100
The Great Master Buddha
invited me this time.

105
00:10:39,100 --> 00:10:40,430
Put this meal on his tab.

106
00:10:40,580 --> 00:10:41,080
Here.

107
00:10:41,270 --> 00:10:42,870
Here are your noodles.

108
00:10:43,270 --> 00:10:44,270
Enjoy your meals.

109
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:48,080
What are you looking at? Get to work.

110
00:10:49,330 --> 00:10:49,880
Mentor,

111
00:10:53,240 --> 00:10:55,770
do you really believe
what Zhang Qishan said?

112
00:10:56,890 --> 00:10:59,350
Shrimpie massacred the Mo faction warlords

113
00:11:00,530 --> 00:11:02,100
and almost harmed the Zhang family.

114
00:11:02,100 --> 00:11:04,600
You said you felt Zhang Haixia
had changed.

115
00:11:05,240 --> 00:11:06,390
For all we know, this might

116
00:11:06,390 --> 00:11:07,320
be his fault.

117
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:10,730
Is it because of that medicine?

118
00:11:11,460 --> 00:11:14,190
Does that medicine
have such major side effects?

119
00:11:21,150 --> 00:11:23,880
Let's find Zhang Haixia
and bring him back first.

120
00:11:25,890 --> 00:11:28,220
But you also need to prepare
for the worst.

121
00:11:29,630 --> 00:11:30,890
Prepare for the worst?

122
00:11:31,790 --> 00:11:32,720
What do you mean?

123
00:11:34,170 --> 00:11:35,770
You have a white hair strand.

124
00:11:37,130 --> 00:11:37,790
Where?

125
00:11:50,860 --> 00:11:53,060
I'm over a hundred years old, after all.

126
00:11:56,600 --> 00:11:59,250
More than a hundred.
You can live for a thousand years.

127
00:11:59,250 --> 00:12:00,710
Do you think I'm a monster?

128
00:12:01,820 --> 00:12:02,750
Let's eat first.

129
00:12:04,630 --> 00:12:05,220
Is it ready?

130
00:12:05,220 --> 00:12:05,880
It's ready.

131
00:12:06,340 --> 00:12:07,070
Extra spicy.

132
00:12:08,730 --> 00:12:09,190
Please.

133
00:12:18,940 --> 00:12:19,530
Mentor.

134
00:12:33,050 --> 00:12:34,310
What's wrong with her?

135
00:12:36,100 --> 00:12:36,630
Well...

136
00:12:38,840 --> 00:12:40,300
I'm asking you, how is she?

137
00:12:40,980 --> 00:12:42,130
Was she poisoned?

138
00:12:43,650 --> 00:12:45,510
She was exposed to poison before.

139
00:12:46,010 --> 00:12:46,600
Well...

140
00:12:47,360 --> 00:12:49,370
It doesn't seem like she was poisoned.

141
00:12:49,370 --> 00:12:50,050
Why are you hesitating?

142
00:12:50,050 --> 00:12:51,480
I'm asking you, what's wrong with her?

143
00:12:51,480 --> 00:12:53,890
Your sister's pulse is very strange.

144
00:12:54,180 --> 00:12:55,930
She looks young,

145
00:12:56,240 --> 00:12:59,150
but her pulse is like a 70-year-old's.

146
00:12:59,170 --> 00:13:00,070
What else?

147
00:13:01,240 --> 00:13:02,300
Nothing else.

148
00:13:02,330 --> 00:13:04,390
But a pulse like that in a young person

149
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:06,340
is extremely strange.

150
00:13:07,580 --> 00:13:09,480
Then why won't she wake up?

151
00:13:10,370 --> 00:13:11,810
She's probably too tired.

152
00:13:11,810 --> 00:13:14,410
She should be fine
after resting for a few days.

153
00:13:14,900 --> 00:13:16,450
She's obviously unconscious now,

154
00:13:16,450 --> 00:13:17,460
and you're telling me she's fine?

155
00:13:17,460 --> 00:13:18,290
Are you kidding me?

156
00:13:18,290 --> 00:13:18,890
Wait, I...

157
00:13:18,940 --> 00:13:19,440
Get out!

158
00:13:19,860 --> 00:13:20,360
Okay.

159
00:13:49,170 --> 00:13:49,970
[Report]

160
00:13:49,620 --> 00:13:50,120
Great Master Buddha,

161
00:13:49,970 --> 00:13:50,580
[Zhang family
corpse-cultivated grass toxin]

162
00:13:50,600 --> 00:13:51,510
[Concentration: three times
that of a normal sample]

163
00:13:50,770 --> 00:13:51,890
Mo Yungao's bases

164
00:13:51,940 --> 00:13:53,270
have all been breached.

165
00:13:53,500 --> 00:13:54,560
All Twilight Grass

166
00:13:54,630 --> 00:13:56,030
has also been destroyed.

167
00:13:57,290 --> 00:13:59,620
Mo Yungao has already tried it in Nanyang?

168
00:13:59,770 --> 00:14:00,250
Yes.

169
00:14:00,480 --> 00:14:01,930
Mo Yungao released it in Nanyang,

170
00:14:01,930 --> 00:14:04,260
and now he wants to release it nationwide.

171
00:14:05,790 --> 00:14:06,600
I'm afraid

172
00:14:06,750 --> 00:14:08,680
he wants to cause greater turmoil.

173
00:14:10,590 --> 00:14:12,720
If he's really coming for that person,

174
00:14:13,550 --> 00:14:15,410
he probably won't give up easily.

175
00:14:15,870 --> 00:14:17,320
He will likely regroup

176
00:14:17,850 --> 00:14:19,580
and cause even bigger trouble.

177
00:14:20,820 --> 00:14:22,420
Keeping this Mo Yungao alive

178
00:14:22,620 --> 00:14:23,870
is a disaster.

179
00:14:26,150 --> 00:14:28,390
Unfortunately, my hands
are tied right now.

180
00:14:28,390 --> 00:14:29,440
Zhang Haiqi and the others

181
00:14:29,440 --> 00:14:30,500
are on their own.

182
00:14:30,960 --> 00:14:31,500
Report!

183
00:14:32,200 --> 00:14:32,700
Speak.

184
00:14:32,910 --> 00:14:33,540
Great Master Buddha,

185
00:14:33,540 --> 00:14:35,110
someone claiming to be your poor relative

186
00:14:35,110 --> 00:14:37,970
is asking to see you
about a matter of life and death.

187
00:14:40,590 --> 00:14:43,310
[Silence]

188
00:14:46,700 --> 00:14:48,940
[Silence]

189
00:15:24,900 --> 00:15:25,960
We found the cause.

190
00:15:27,590 --> 00:15:31,900
[Report]

191
00:15:28,890 --> 00:15:31,550
Here's the information
we found from Mo Yungao.

192
00:15:32,010 --> 00:15:33,360
Zhang Haiqi was poisoned

193
00:15:33,360 --> 00:15:34,960
by a special alkaloid.

194
00:15:35,980 --> 00:15:38,000
While cultivating Twilight Grass,

195
00:15:38,360 --> 00:15:42,020
he accidentally discovered
that its flowers were far more toxic.

196
00:15:42,270 --> 00:15:43,670
So he ground them for use.

197
00:15:45,200 --> 00:15:47,200
The yield of this flower is very low,

198
00:15:47,260 --> 00:15:49,390
and it is extremely hard to cultivate.

199
00:15:50,000 --> 00:15:52,060
But its potency is extremely strong.

200
00:15:52,320 --> 00:15:55,780
It can be used against
high-level members of the Zhang family.

201
00:15:56,250 --> 00:15:58,850
He only ground a small bottle of
poison powder,

202
00:15:59,420 --> 00:16:01,890
and used it all on Zhang Haiqi.

203
00:16:02,240 --> 00:16:03,650
Regarding the mechanism
that destroys the body,

204
00:16:03,650 --> 00:16:04,350
well,

205
00:16:05,250 --> 00:16:06,780
how bad will this situation

206
00:16:07,030 --> 00:16:07,860
get?

207
00:16:08,980 --> 00:16:11,400
Her whole body is aging rapidly now.

208
00:16:13,340 --> 00:16:14,540
Within three months,

209
00:16:15,030 --> 00:16:17,050
she will die of organ failure.

210
00:16:24,500 --> 00:16:27,600
Aren't the Zhang family members
supposed to have special physiques?

211
00:16:27,600 --> 00:16:29,870
Is there no special treatment?

212
00:16:30,130 --> 00:16:32,320
The Zhang family's origins

213
00:16:32,370 --> 00:16:33,900
have always been a mystery.

214
00:16:34,470 --> 00:16:37,820
Even the Zhang family members
themselves don't know much about it.

215
00:16:37,820 --> 00:16:39,820
If we want things to turn around now,

216
00:16:40,150 --> 00:16:41,880
there's only one possibility.

217
00:16:42,050 --> 00:16:43,850
We have to find their patriarch.

218
00:16:45,480 --> 00:16:46,480
The patriarch of the Zhang family?

219
00:16:46,480 --> 00:16:48,080
The head of the Zhang family.

220
00:16:48,880 --> 00:16:49,660
Where is he?

221
00:16:50,390 --> 00:16:52,700
The Zhang family patriarch
has been missing for a long time.

222
00:16:52,700 --> 00:16:54,670
He was last seen in Bailejing.

223
00:16:54,870 --> 00:16:55,750
Bailejing.

224
00:16:56,400 --> 00:16:58,190
Bailejing covers a vast area

225
00:16:58,220 --> 00:17:00,550
with hundreds of thousands of mountains.

226
00:17:01,100 --> 00:17:03,080
The actions of the Zhang family patriarch

227
00:17:03,080 --> 00:17:04,829
have always been mysterious
and unpredictable.

228
00:17:04,829 --> 00:17:06,069
Even the Zhang family members

229
00:17:06,069 --> 00:17:07,670
might not be able to find him.

230
00:17:09,740 --> 00:17:10,250
Okay.

231
00:17:14,240 --> 00:17:16,200
This is the report
on the Twilight Grass spread incident.

232
00:17:14,609 --> 00:17:16,369
[Case File]

233
00:17:16,680 --> 00:17:17,890
If she wakes up,

234
00:17:18,420 --> 00:17:19,220
show it to her.

235
00:17:20,880 --> 00:17:21,770
This matter

236
00:17:22,460 --> 00:17:24,660
can be considered to have come to an end.

237
00:18:16,640 --> 00:18:17,370
Mentor.

238
00:18:18,400 --> 00:18:19,200
You're awake.

239
00:18:20,310 --> 00:18:20,790
Yeah.

240
00:18:21,770 --> 00:18:23,100
How long have I been out?

241
00:18:24,160 --> 00:18:24,850
Three days.

242
00:18:25,290 --> 00:18:26,160
How do you feel?

243
00:18:26,550 --> 00:18:27,680
I'll go get a doctor.

244
00:18:27,770 --> 00:18:28,830
Pour me some water.

245
00:18:28,900 --> 00:18:29,630
I'm thirsty.

246
00:18:29,810 --> 00:18:30,240
Okay.

247
00:18:31,440 --> 00:18:32,900
Do you want to sit up first?

248
00:18:45,610 --> 00:18:48,210
Zhang Qishan came
while you were unconscious.

249
00:18:48,740 --> 00:18:49,850
He said

250
00:18:51,160 --> 00:18:53,690
it was Mo Yungao
who poisoned you on the train.

251
00:18:54,380 --> 00:18:55,420
He also left a document

252
00:18:55,420 --> 00:18:57,010
for you to read when you wake up.

253
00:18:57,010 --> 00:18:58,340
Drink some water first.

254
00:18:58,920 --> 00:18:59,530
Careful, it's hot.

255
00:18:59,530 --> 00:18:59,990
Mm.

256
00:19:06,410 --> 00:19:07,980
I have a general idea.

257
00:19:09,020 --> 00:19:11,420
I was still a bit conscious
during the coma,

258
00:19:11,720 --> 00:19:13,650
hearing you talk intermittently.

259
00:19:14,400 --> 00:19:16,260
This poison in me cannot be cured.

260
00:19:17,720 --> 00:19:18,660
Who said that?

261
00:19:19,570 --> 00:19:21,170
He said the only way to cure it

262
00:19:21,530 --> 00:19:24,730
is to go to Bailejing
and find the Zhang family patriarch.

263
00:19:24,920 --> 00:19:26,220
You're awake now.

264
00:19:26,480 --> 00:19:30,480
-Let's go to Bailejing tomorrow.
-Is there any news about Zhang Haixia?

265
00:19:36,880 --> 00:19:37,930
Zhang Haixia

266
00:19:39,640 --> 00:19:41,460
probably planned his escape route
very early on,

267
00:19:41,460 --> 00:19:43,190
and did anti-reconnaissance,

268
00:19:43,700 --> 00:19:45,250
clearing all the traces he left behind.

269
00:19:45,250 --> 00:19:47,450
Zhang Qishan couldn't find him either.

270
00:19:50,220 --> 00:19:51,690
Now that he's gone,

271
00:19:52,030 --> 00:19:53,560
what are you planning to do?

272
00:20:02,440 --> 00:20:03,770
What am I planning to do?

273
00:20:06,980 --> 00:20:07,770
I'll just bring him back

274
00:20:07,770 --> 00:20:08,680
and talk to him.

275
00:20:10,640 --> 00:20:12,030
If he has really lost his mind,

276
00:20:12,030 --> 00:20:12,940
I'll fix him.

277
00:20:16,190 --> 00:20:18,050
Although I know you won't listen,

278
00:20:18,720 --> 00:20:20,450
I advise you not to look for him.

279
00:20:21,480 --> 00:20:23,960
If something is really wrong
with Zhang Haixia,

280
00:20:23,960 --> 00:20:25,190
or he even turns evil,

281
00:20:26,590 --> 00:20:27,500
then you will have to face the situation

282
00:20:27,500 --> 00:20:29,830
of whether to kill him
with your own hands.

283
00:20:31,480 --> 00:20:32,940
I don't think you can do it.

284
00:20:35,160 --> 00:20:36,730
So if you go after him,

285
00:20:37,500 --> 00:20:39,140
it won't end well for you.

286
00:20:43,480 --> 00:20:44,760
Is your brain fried from the fever?

287
00:20:44,760 --> 00:20:47,010
Why don't you listen to
what you're saying?

288
00:20:47,010 --> 00:20:48,610
I was just making an analogy.

289
00:20:49,530 --> 00:20:52,060
You always lose your cool
when it comes to him.

290
00:20:52,610 --> 00:20:54,010
I'm not like that now.

291
00:20:58,250 --> 00:21:00,850
Shrimpie must have his reasons
for doing this.

292
00:21:04,640 --> 00:21:06,240
If he really became like this

293
00:21:08,330 --> 00:21:09,640
because of that drug,

294
00:21:09,740 --> 00:21:11,940
then I have even more reason to cure him—

295
00:21:12,700 --> 00:21:13,760
because I'm the one

296
00:21:14,960 --> 00:21:16,760
who caused this to happen to him.

297
00:21:18,740 --> 00:21:20,200
That's not guilt talking.

298
00:21:21,480 --> 00:21:23,080
That's just your obsession.

299
00:21:26,850 --> 00:21:29,510
Enough. That's not what's
important right now.

300
00:21:29,900 --> 00:21:32,030
Right now, the most important thing is

301
00:21:32,720 --> 00:21:34,380
to help you find the medicine.

302
00:21:34,460 --> 00:21:35,850
Then we'll head to Bailejing

303
00:21:35,850 --> 00:21:37,050
and bring Shrimpie back.

304
00:21:37,050 --> 00:21:39,050
-Shrimpie...
-Then there's even less reason to.

305
00:21:39,050 --> 00:21:40,580
I'm not going to Bailejing.

306
00:21:43,740 --> 00:21:44,530
Why not?

307
00:21:46,970 --> 00:21:47,790
This time,

308
00:21:48,570 --> 00:21:49,480
I will die.

309
00:21:56,820 --> 00:21:57,220
You...

310
00:21:59,460 --> 00:22:00,660
Why are you like this?

311
00:22:02,040 --> 00:22:02,770
Mentor,

312
00:22:02,790 --> 00:22:04,380
can you not be like Zhang Haixia,

313
00:22:04,380 --> 00:22:06,040
so immature and disobedient?

314
00:22:08,240 --> 00:22:09,570
It makes me so tired.

315
00:22:12,360 --> 00:22:14,290
I know what's happening to my body.

316
00:22:16,570 --> 00:22:19,430
Endless youth isn't something
I can enjoy forever.

317
00:22:22,940 --> 00:22:24,940
I've lived for over a hundred years—

318
00:22:26,550 --> 00:22:28,610
my life has been long and full enough.

319
00:22:30,590 --> 00:22:32,370
These days, death isn't

320
00:22:33,010 --> 00:22:34,010
something I fear.

321
00:22:35,220 --> 00:22:37,020
If anything, it feels peaceful,

322
00:22:37,420 --> 00:22:38,550
and even welcome.

323
00:22:47,660 --> 00:22:48,310
Yes,

324
00:22:49,200 --> 00:22:50,730
you are quite open-minded.

325
00:22:51,810 --> 00:22:52,660
You're basically an old lady

326
00:22:52,660 --> 00:22:54,610
who has already lived a whole lifetime.

327
00:22:54,610 --> 00:22:55,400
I'm different from you.

328
00:22:55,400 --> 00:22:56,330
I'm still young.

329
00:22:56,830 --> 00:22:57,310
Don't worry about it.

330
00:22:57,310 --> 00:22:59,170
I'll go find the medicine for you.

331
00:22:59,940 --> 00:23:01,870
Then I'll bring Zhang Haixia back.

332
00:23:03,160 --> 00:23:04,420
That's your business.

333
00:23:15,380 --> 00:23:17,380
We're bound to part sooner or later.

334
00:23:18,270 --> 00:23:19,720
It's just happening

335
00:23:20,400 --> 00:23:22,130
a little sooner than expected.

336
00:23:23,770 --> 00:23:25,180
At least give it a try.

337
00:23:26,200 --> 00:23:27,050
Just try it.

338
00:23:27,050 --> 00:23:27,770
Do it for me.

339
00:23:27,770 --> 00:23:29,530
Can't you live for me?

340
00:23:32,640 --> 00:23:34,330
How dare you say that to me?

341
00:23:37,140 --> 00:23:38,400
Then for Zhang Haixia.

342
00:23:39,220 --> 00:23:41,080
Don't you care about him the most?

343
00:23:46,660 --> 00:23:48,050
Do you want to just watch him

344
00:23:48,050 --> 00:23:49,250
lose the will to go on?

345
00:23:53,700 --> 00:23:57,430
Is growing taller the only thing
you've accomplished these years?

346
00:23:59,270 --> 00:24:00,610
I'm tired. Get out.

347
00:24:05,070 --> 00:24:05,740
Get out.

348
00:24:11,100 --> 00:24:12,420
Remember to read the documents.

349
00:24:12,420 --> 00:24:15,020
I'll go buy you some rice noodles.
Extra spicy.

350
00:25:07,290 --> 00:25:10,150
Two bowls of rice noodles.
Pack one up. Extra spicy.

351
00:25:11,340 --> 00:25:16,070
[Changxiang Rice Noodles]

352
00:25:17,000 --> 00:25:19,000
Why is this troublemaker back again?

353
00:25:19,000 --> 00:25:20,160
Hurry up and make him a bowl of noodles.

354
00:25:20,160 --> 00:25:21,610
Let him eat and leave quickly.

355
00:25:21,610 --> 00:25:22,940
This guy has been here twice.

356
00:25:22,940 --> 00:25:24,070
Once he offended the officials

357
00:25:24,070 --> 00:25:25,830
and completely smashed up my stall.

358
00:25:25,830 --> 00:25:26,680
Another time,

359
00:25:26,740 --> 00:25:28,200
someone almost died here.

360
00:25:28,240 --> 00:25:28,810
This time,

361
00:25:28,810 --> 00:25:30,810
who knows what trouble he'll cause.

362
00:25:34,570 --> 00:25:35,220
Sir,

363
00:25:35,790 --> 00:25:37,480
you really like eating rice noodles.

364
00:25:37,480 --> 00:25:39,400
The girl who was with you last time—

365
00:25:39,400 --> 00:25:40,140
I saw her pass out.

366
00:25:40,140 --> 00:25:41,220
Is she okay now?

367
00:25:41,220 --> 00:25:43,160
If she were dying, could you save her?

368
00:25:43,160 --> 00:25:44,220
Noodles are ready.

369
00:25:50,530 --> 00:25:51,480
Here you go, sir.

370
00:25:52,010 --> 00:25:52,760
Extra spicy.

371
00:26:13,030 --> 00:26:14,960
Water, water, water. Out of water.

372
00:26:15,050 --> 00:26:15,640
Okay.

373
00:26:18,510 --> 00:26:19,370
Too spicy?

374
00:26:19,610 --> 00:26:22,790
Didn't you say we don't have
chili peppers in Changxiang?

375
00:26:22,790 --> 00:26:24,590
Did I say your noodles are spicy?

376
00:26:24,660 --> 00:26:25,770
Did I say your noodles are spicy?

377
00:26:25,770 --> 00:26:26,500
No, no, no.

378
00:26:26,500 --> 00:26:27,430
What's going on?

379
00:26:27,530 --> 00:26:28,700
I'm gonna smash your sign to pieces!

380
00:26:28,700 --> 00:26:29,810
I'll go get water.

381
00:26:31,350 --> 00:26:32,050
What?

382
00:26:32,720 --> 00:26:34,850
You want to smash our Changxiang sign?

383
00:26:37,000 --> 00:26:38,600
Great Master Buddha is here.

384
00:26:38,740 --> 00:26:39,740
Here's the water.

385
00:26:40,460 --> 00:26:41,450
A bowl of noodles.

386
00:26:41,450 --> 00:26:41,950
Okay.

387
00:26:45,050 --> 00:26:46,830
The first time I came to Changxiang,

388
00:26:46,830 --> 00:26:48,830
I ate the noodles made by this owner,

389
00:26:50,050 --> 00:26:52,580
and decided to stay.

390
00:26:56,610 --> 00:26:58,740
Enjoy your meal, Great Master Buddha.

391
00:27:13,290 --> 00:27:14,760
Since I left the North,

392
00:27:15,250 --> 00:27:17,980
I haven't had any contact
with the Zhang family.

393
00:27:19,720 --> 00:27:21,510
You're the first distant relative

394
00:27:21,510 --> 00:27:23,110
I've seen in all these years.

395
00:27:23,290 --> 00:27:24,890
It does bring back memories.

396
00:27:25,200 --> 00:27:26,330
Three relatives...

397
00:27:28,030 --> 00:27:29,830
Soon, there'll only be one left.

398
00:27:32,700 --> 00:27:34,030
My mentor is gravely ill

399
00:27:34,750 --> 00:27:35,570
and dying.

400
00:27:36,220 --> 00:27:38,610
She's given up
and is just waiting for the end.

401
00:27:38,610 --> 00:27:39,720
That brother of mine went crazy.

402
00:27:39,720 --> 00:27:41,520
I don't even know where he is now.

403
00:27:43,530 --> 00:27:45,590
I still have to help you find someone,

404
00:27:46,850 --> 00:27:48,580
and treat my mentor's illness.

405
00:27:55,900 --> 00:27:56,860
But what if?

406
00:27:59,680 --> 00:28:00,680
I mean, what if...

407
00:28:01,220 --> 00:28:03,550
What if my brother
has truly lost his mind?

408
00:28:04,000 --> 00:28:05,330
What am I supposed to do?

409
00:28:05,660 --> 00:28:07,990
When dealing with someone who's gone mad,

410
00:28:08,330 --> 00:28:10,370
the best way to calm them down

411
00:28:10,400 --> 00:28:12,460
is not to treat them like they're mad.

412
00:28:13,900 --> 00:28:15,110
Make him feel

413
00:28:15,900 --> 00:28:17,570
that nothing has changed.

414
00:28:18,740 --> 00:28:20,070
If they've done terrible things,

415
00:28:20,070 --> 00:28:22,000
pretend you don't know about them.

416
00:28:24,330 --> 00:28:25,140
Why?

417
00:28:26,090 --> 00:28:27,180
Because right now,

418
00:28:28,590 --> 00:28:29,840
if he thinks

419
00:28:30,030 --> 00:28:32,010
he can still be with you like before,

420
00:28:32,010 --> 00:28:33,180
the good in him

421
00:28:34,610 --> 00:28:36,270
still has a reason to survive.

422
00:28:36,570 --> 00:28:38,700
But if you've already started to hate him,

423
00:28:38,700 --> 00:28:40,010
or if he comes to believe that

424
00:28:40,010 --> 00:28:40,980
the good in him

425
00:28:40,980 --> 00:28:42,570
has no hope left,

426
00:28:43,590 --> 00:28:46,250
then that goodness
will disappear completely.

427
00:28:47,030 --> 00:28:49,230
He will become an evil spirit from hell.

428
00:28:50,770 --> 00:28:51,400
So,

429
00:28:52,480 --> 00:28:54,220
you must act as if nothing

430
00:28:55,200 --> 00:28:56,380
has happened.

431
00:29:41,530 --> 00:29:43,190
You don't need to persuade me.

432
00:29:43,250 --> 00:29:44,660
I won't go to Bailejing.

433
00:29:45,110 --> 00:29:47,320
I am Qi Tiezui from the Nine Clans.

434
00:29:47,510 --> 00:29:48,810
I'm talking about you.

435
00:29:49,770 --> 00:29:50,380
Miss,

436
00:29:51,400 --> 00:29:52,590
that little kid of yours

437
00:29:52,590 --> 00:29:53,920
is at Great Master Buddha's residence.

438
00:29:53,920 --> 00:29:55,570
He has been making a fuss for days.

439
00:29:55,570 --> 00:29:57,500
Great Master Buddha specifically asked me

440
00:29:57,500 --> 00:29:59,100
to come have a word with you.

441
00:29:59,270 --> 00:29:59,980
No need.

442
00:30:01,530 --> 00:30:02,910
Just a chat.

443
00:30:03,310 --> 00:30:04,890
You have nothing to lose.

444
00:30:05,460 --> 00:30:06,660
You are older.

445
00:30:07,420 --> 00:30:09,050
You've learned to take things in stride.

446
00:30:09,050 --> 00:30:10,600
But the young ones

447
00:30:10,750 --> 00:30:12,550
might not think things through.

448
00:30:12,750 --> 00:30:13,500
Besides,

449
00:30:14,590 --> 00:30:16,200
I took six wen from you.

450
00:30:16,700 --> 00:30:18,500
I can't just take it for nothing.

451
00:30:20,180 --> 00:30:21,040
How about this?

452
00:30:21,850 --> 00:30:22,900
Let's play

453
00:30:24,530 --> 00:30:27,010
a little folk game today, shall we?

454
00:30:29,700 --> 00:30:30,710
How old are you?

455
00:30:30,940 --> 00:30:32,670
You're never too old for a game.

456
00:30:32,790 --> 00:30:33,330
Besides,

457
00:30:34,160 --> 00:30:35,450
those kids of yours

458
00:30:35,480 --> 00:30:37,410
practically burned my place down.

459
00:30:38,110 --> 00:30:39,810
Just consider it comforting me,

460
00:30:39,810 --> 00:30:40,740
making me happy.

461
00:30:40,790 --> 00:30:41,590
Please cooperate.

462
00:30:41,590 --> 00:30:42,350
Alright.

463
00:30:42,920 --> 00:30:44,680
South. Seven across, eight down.

464
00:30:44,680 --> 00:30:45,280
All right.

465
00:30:45,380 --> 00:30:48,330
South. Seven across, eight down.

466
00:30:50,850 --> 00:30:55,650
An old blossom blooms anew.
Dead branches welcome spring once more.

467
00:30:58,380 --> 00:31:02,360
Old grudges fade,
and old loves drift away with the tide.

468
00:31:02,570 --> 00:31:04,180
A withered branch falls from the tree,

469
00:31:04,180 --> 00:31:06,740
It falls under the tree, rolls three times,
lands at its roots, and rolls three times.

470
00:31:06,740 --> 00:31:08,460
Gain and loss, both at their peak.

471
00:31:08,460 --> 00:31:09,660
What it means is this:

472
00:31:10,160 --> 00:31:11,850
the best and worst moments

473
00:31:11,980 --> 00:31:12,980
in a person's life

474
00:31:13,420 --> 00:31:15,350
reach their peaks at the same time.

475
00:31:15,510 --> 00:31:16,510
You chose "South"

476
00:31:16,720 --> 00:31:18,420
right off the bat.

477
00:31:18,940 --> 00:31:22,050
You must have a wonderful encounter
in the south.

478
00:31:22,660 --> 00:31:24,720
What if I don't want to go to the south?

479
00:31:25,680 --> 00:31:26,850
Things change.

480
00:31:27,570 --> 00:31:29,830
If one day you suddenly don't want to die,

481
00:31:30,310 --> 00:31:32,840
it's best to be on the path of
saving yourself.

482
00:31:33,250 --> 00:31:34,110
Do you people of the Nine Clans

483
00:31:34,110 --> 00:31:36,510
always like to meddle in others' business?

484
00:31:38,700 --> 00:31:40,810
I had a piece of fruit

485
00:31:40,900 --> 00:31:42,980
at the Great Master Buddha's
residence once.
It was delicious.

486
00:31:42,980 --> 00:31:44,640
I hear it comes from Xiacheng.

487
00:31:45,000 --> 00:31:46,260
If you're still alive,

488
00:31:47,570 --> 00:31:49,230
you might as well send me some.

489
00:31:56,420 --> 00:31:57,880
Never mind saving myself.

490
00:31:57,960 --> 00:31:59,820
Gain and loss, both at their peak?

491
00:32:25,980 --> 00:32:26,640
Commander,

492
00:32:27,050 --> 00:32:29,350
Beilian's base has also been occupied
by Zhang Qishan.

493
00:32:29,350 --> 00:32:31,160
He is still sending troops
to search for us.

494
00:32:31,160 --> 00:32:31,750
We

495
00:32:32,180 --> 00:32:32,980
are defeated.

496
00:32:34,720 --> 00:32:35,330
Defeated?

497
00:32:36,530 --> 00:32:37,110
Yes

498
00:32:37,570 --> 00:32:38,900
Are we really defeated?

499
00:32:42,160 --> 00:32:42,960
We really are.

500
00:32:44,720 --> 00:32:45,840
Excellent.

501
00:32:53,650 --> 00:33:01,710
[Academy]

502
00:33:14,310 --> 00:33:15,220
Old gentleman,

503
00:33:16,030 --> 00:33:19,890
people say you're a man who knows all things—
the past and the present,

504
00:33:19,920 --> 00:33:21,350
the hearts of men,

505
00:33:21,940 --> 00:33:25,270
even the workings of fate.
And that you've never been wrong.

506
00:33:25,550 --> 00:33:27,210
It took me quite a bit of effort

507
00:33:27,680 --> 00:33:30,950
to track you down.

508
00:33:41,770 --> 00:33:43,480
So I'd like to ask you something.

509
00:33:43,480 --> 00:33:44,550
Right here,

510
00:33:44,940 --> 00:33:45,740
and right now—

511
00:33:45,880 --> 00:33:46,610
are you

512
00:33:47,330 --> 00:33:48,160
going to

513
00:33:49,250 --> 00:33:50,250
die or

514
00:33:51,810 --> 00:33:52,910
live?

515
00:33:53,810 --> 00:33:55,110
Die.

516
00:33:55,620 --> 00:33:57,320
[Academy]

517
00:34:12,030 --> 00:34:13,730
You figured it out.

518
00:34:22,760 --> 00:34:25,219
I've decided not to kill you.

519
00:34:25,440 --> 00:34:28,449
Your reputation as an immortal is ruined.

520
00:34:29,860 --> 00:34:31,750
It's just an empty title.

521
00:34:31,940 --> 00:34:33,870
Destined friend,

522
00:34:34,010 --> 00:34:35,070
may I ask,

523
00:34:36,230 --> 00:34:40,420
are you here for something else?

524
00:34:43,760 --> 00:34:45,020
You've got something.

525
00:34:49,340 --> 00:34:50,870
I do have

526
00:34:51,480 --> 00:34:53,300
a big plan to execute,

527
00:34:53,960 --> 00:34:55,460
but it's a bit complicated

528
00:34:57,090 --> 00:34:57,960
and tricky.

529
00:34:58,820 --> 00:35:00,370
So read my fortune.

530
00:35:00,610 --> 00:35:01,960
When

531
00:35:02,510 --> 00:35:04,510
and how can I achieve great success?

532
00:35:05,860 --> 00:35:07,010
Wait until

533
00:35:07,840 --> 00:35:10,300
three of your generals meet their end

534
00:35:10,960 --> 00:35:13,120
and you suffer one crushing defeat;

535
00:35:13,630 --> 00:35:16,160
then your grand design
will finally succeed.

536
00:35:16,690 --> 00:35:19,380
Three generals lost and one defeat.

537
00:35:19,900 --> 00:35:21,520
That means

538
00:35:21,760 --> 00:35:25,230
I will lose three great generals

539
00:35:25,670 --> 00:35:27,780
and suffer one defeat

540
00:35:28,400 --> 00:35:29,690
before I achieve great success.

541
00:35:29,690 --> 00:35:30,890
Is that what you mean?

542
00:35:57,980 --> 00:35:59,110
He's really dead.

543
00:36:00,440 --> 00:36:02,000
He really is an immortal.

544
00:36:02,000 --> 00:36:02,590
Sir.

545
00:36:03,940 --> 00:36:05,180
He's got something.

546
00:36:07,210 --> 00:36:08,380
He's got something.

547
00:36:08,800 --> 00:36:10,590
You are his students.
Why aren't you crying?

548
00:36:10,590 --> 00:36:11,480
Cry out loud!

549
00:36:12,460 --> 00:36:13,510
Sir!

550
00:36:15,820 --> 00:36:17,550
This place is quite something.

551
00:36:22,090 --> 00:36:24,880
Wait until three of your generals
meet their end

552
00:36:25,170 --> 00:36:28,650
and you suffer one crushing defeat;
then your grand design will finally succeed.

553
00:36:28,650 --> 00:36:31,490
I've already lost two lieutenants

554
00:36:31,590 --> 00:36:33,270
and suffered this defeat.

555
00:36:33,960 --> 00:36:36,020
If I lose one more lieutenant,

556
00:36:36,390 --> 00:36:38,250
my grand scheme will be complete.

557
00:36:43,690 --> 00:36:44,440
Commander.

558
00:36:46,690 --> 00:36:47,690
Are you

559
00:36:47,920 --> 00:36:51,480
willing to be my last lieutenant?

560
00:36:52,630 --> 00:36:53,230
Me?

561
00:36:54,000 --> 00:36:55,020
Am I qualified?

562
00:36:55,130 --> 00:36:55,980
Yes, you are.

563
00:36:56,630 --> 00:36:58,990
Thank you for the promotion,
Commander. I am willing.

564
00:36:58,990 --> 00:37:00,490
You're quite agreeable.

565
00:37:01,880 --> 00:37:03,140
Thank you, Commander.

566
00:37:03,510 --> 00:37:04,640
You're thanking me?

567
00:37:05,550 --> 00:37:06,210
Commander,

568
00:37:06,840 --> 00:37:07,860
with the snake medicine,

569
00:37:07,860 --> 00:37:10,060
it seems your wounds are almost healed.

570
00:37:12,170 --> 00:37:13,960
This guy has some tricks.

571
00:37:12,290 --> 00:37:14,810
[Snake Patriarch, Mo Yungao
Recruits Men of Talent]

572
00:37:15,390 --> 00:37:17,590
He also used snakes to scout and report,

573
00:37:17,800 --> 00:37:19,690
so we knew Zhang Qishan was coming.

574
00:37:19,690 --> 00:37:22,150
We managed to evacuate
from the base in time.

575
00:37:22,170 --> 00:37:24,210
He's just acting a bit weird.

576
00:37:24,380 --> 00:37:25,260
Whatever I ask him,

577
00:37:25,260 --> 00:37:26,320
he won't say a word.

578
00:37:27,420 --> 00:37:28,760
Should I...

579
00:37:28,900 --> 00:37:30,100
Why would he tell you?

580
00:37:30,300 --> 00:37:31,630
Who do you think you are?

581
00:37:33,570 --> 00:37:34,630
I spoke out of turn.

582
00:37:35,760 --> 00:37:37,400
Is  Zhang Haiqi

583
00:37:38,460 --> 00:37:39,260
dead?

584
00:37:40,320 --> 00:37:41,010
No.

585
00:37:41,760 --> 00:37:43,680
I have never seen this before.

586
00:37:43,960 --> 00:37:46,420
Usually, after members of the Zhang family
are poisoned,

587
00:37:46,420 --> 00:37:47,940
they immediately become paralyzed.

588
00:37:47,940 --> 00:37:49,650
They would die within three days.

589
00:37:49,650 --> 00:37:51,540
After Zhang Haiqi was poisoned,

590
00:37:51,730 --> 00:37:53,010
not only did she not die,

591
00:37:53,010 --> 00:37:54,500
but she also planned a long trip.

592
00:37:54,500 --> 00:37:57,380
So she is just like that person,

593
00:37:57,980 --> 00:38:01,650
a different member of the Zhang family.

594
00:38:01,710 --> 00:38:04,070
But the Twilight Grass flower
must be effective.

595
00:38:04,070 --> 00:38:05,530
Her condition is not good.

596
00:38:08,780 --> 00:38:10,550
Ever since I knew you were Zhang Haiqi,

597
00:38:10,550 --> 00:38:11,920
I opened it.

598
00:38:12,400 --> 00:38:13,360
Under your sofa,

599
00:38:13,820 --> 00:38:14,530
there is another bottle

600
00:38:14,530 --> 00:38:15,860
with a stronger effect.

601
00:38:17,030 --> 00:38:17,590
Alright.

602
00:38:18,300 --> 00:38:19,120
However,

603
00:38:19,920 --> 00:38:21,840
she won't live much longer anyway.

604
00:38:21,840 --> 00:38:24,130
Poisoned by the Twilight Grass flower,

605
00:38:25,980 --> 00:38:27,380
she will definitely die.

606
00:38:30,800 --> 00:38:31,440
Report!

607
00:38:36,550 --> 00:38:37,210
Commander,

608
00:38:37,420 --> 00:38:39,220
Mr. Zhang has been brought here.

609
00:38:39,480 --> 00:38:41,010
What about the other group?

610
00:38:41,070 --> 00:38:41,730
Commander,

611
00:38:42,000 --> 00:38:43,330
they have returned too.

612
00:38:47,130 --> 00:38:47,920
Commander,

613
00:38:48,360 --> 00:38:49,760
I'm glad you're alright.

614
00:39:14,090 --> 00:39:15,470
Our planting base

615
00:39:15,880 --> 00:39:16,920
and seedlings

616
00:39:17,380 --> 00:39:18,550
were all destroyed.

617
00:39:18,840 --> 00:39:20,570
It was done by the Zhang family.

618
00:39:20,980 --> 00:39:21,790
Commander,

619
00:39:22,130 --> 00:39:24,930
although the Twilight Grass plan
failed this time

620
00:39:25,110 --> 00:39:27,310
and re-cultivating the Twilight Grass

621
00:39:27,360 --> 00:39:29,440
will take a lot of time and money,

622
00:39:29,710 --> 00:39:30,650
I am confident.

623
00:39:31,820 --> 00:39:33,020
These funds,

624
00:39:33,530 --> 00:39:35,570
which I have already laundered,

625
00:39:35,820 --> 00:39:38,130
can be used to continue
planting Twilight Grass.

626
00:39:38,130 --> 00:39:39,570
The current situation is chaotic anyway,

627
00:39:39,570 --> 00:39:40,830
so they won't find out.

628
00:39:42,280 --> 00:39:42,820
Also,

629
00:39:43,420 --> 00:39:44,440
do you remember?

630
00:39:45,190 --> 00:39:47,060
We built another base back then,

631
00:39:47,420 --> 00:39:49,590
though it has been abandoned for years.

632
00:39:49,590 --> 00:39:50,990
It's right in Bailejing.

633
00:39:55,000 --> 00:39:56,260
Do you know that

634
00:39:57,590 --> 00:39:59,420
embezzling those public funds

635
00:40:00,480 --> 00:40:02,780
could get me killed a hundred times over?

636
00:40:04,190 --> 00:40:05,670
If this grass this time

637
00:40:05,670 --> 00:40:07,970
still can't lure Zhang Qiling out,

638
00:40:08,550 --> 00:40:10,100
don't you think

639
00:40:10,690 --> 00:40:13,000
we should just die together?

640
00:40:15,400 --> 00:40:18,230
Bailejing.

641
00:40:20,010 --> 00:40:22,530
The first time I fought that guy

642
00:40:22,590 --> 00:40:24,090
was at Bailejing.

643
00:40:24,320 --> 00:40:27,050
Everything for me started there.

644
00:40:27,440 --> 00:40:29,780
Now we are going back to Bailejing.

645
00:40:29,900 --> 00:40:34,630
This is a very, very auspicious sign.

646
00:40:35,840 --> 00:40:38,460
I will definitely find you this time.

